<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-right:-.5in'><span style='font-family:Athenian;
mso-hansi-font-family:Athenian;mso-bidi-font-family:"Times New Roman"'>Borthos
was deep in thought again. He may have to reverse his &quot;no wiping!&quot;
order with the <br>
success of the relatively unstinky Wood Elves. Perhaps the Dwarves should even
take <br>
baths? Hmmm. He could already smell Old Flori with the battle standard from
halfway <br>
across the camp.<br>
<br>
As he absentmindedly stroked his beard crusts from god knows what fell out
unnoticed.<o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-right:-.5in'><span style='font-family:Athenian;
mso-hansi-font-family:Athenian;mso-bidi-font-family:"Times New Roman"'><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>

