damn it!” And stalked off angrily without a backward glance.</p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-right:-.5in'><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-right:-.5in'>Flori shook his head. He could
only hope that The Runehammer and young Olaf Spellbreaker would have greater
success in their upcoming battles.</p>

