<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-right:-.5in'>The Demons had come quickly this
time... the Druchii were ill prepared and<br>
still rallying their scattered forces. The end result was a bloody affair.<br>
This time Orgollithra's forces were not routed, they were cut down by the<br>
